, 35, 41, 1)" bold="true" autoFit="shape-auto-fit"><p><span fontSize="18">一、Nothing账号是什么？—— 生态核心用户资产与变现枢纽</span></p></content></shape><shape width="756" height="48" topLeftX="56.911764705882355" topLeftY="118.23529142491958" type="text" id="bbF"><content fontSize="16" fontFamily="思源黑体" color="rgba(31, 35, 41, 1)" autoFit="shape-auto-fit" wrap="false"><p><strong>打通生态：</strong> 依托统一身份，无缝打通软硬件服务，筑牢生态护城河。</p><p><strong>商业赋能：</strong> 锁定用户留存，沉淀核心数据资产，带动硬件复购与订阅增收，深度挖掘用户的长期商业价值。</p></content></shape><shape width="312" height="54" topLeftX="38.911764705882355" topLeftY="181.76470318962546" type="text" id="bbz"><content textType="sub-headline" fontSize="32" fontFamily="思源黑体" color="rgba(31, 35, 41, 1)" bold="true" autoFit="shape-auto-fit" wrap="false"><p><span fontSize="18">二、Nothing账号2026年目标与挑战？</span></p></content></shape><shape width="520" height="48" topLeftX="59.029411764705884" topLeftY="215.64705613080193" type="text" id="bbI"><content fontSize="16" fontFamily="思源黑体" color="rgba(31, 35, 41, 1)" autoFit="shape-auto-fit" wrap="false"><p><strong>目标：</strong>支撑订阅能力上线及 MCP / Napkin 等业务全面接入。</p><p><strong>挑战：</strong>陈旧的 PHP 架构存在严重安全隐患，难以支撑金融级的安全要求。</p></content></shape><img id="bbh" src="D3pUbEXgToDI9OxWWLmlM35Vgxd" width="871.7549072595488" height="176.41430667619272" topLeftX="38.91176470588232" topLeftY="285.13976518585025"><crop leftOffset="0" rightOffset="0" topOffset="0" bottomOffset="0"/></img></data><note id="bbk"><content/></note></slide>